@node Dtts "MBlank 1.22 - Modules/Petasan/Settings"

	All settings can be set via a settings window or via tooltypes,
	but since the tooltype names do not correspond with their func-
	tion, I advice you to use the settings window, which is much
	more convenient anyway.
@endnode

@node DBugs "MBlank 1.22 - Modules/Petasan/Bugs"


	Petasan has been tested with Enforcer, MungWall and MemWatcher
	and has not generated any hits or memory-loss.

	The glitter effect only glitters on laced screens.
@endnode
